---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <div class="hero" style={`background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)), url('${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}images/hero-bg.webp'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;`}>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Welcome to CRE Trails</h1>
      <p>Explore beautiful multi-use trails in the heart of Chesapeake Ranch Estates</p>
      <div class="btn-group">
        <a href="/map" class="btn btn-primary">View Trail Map</a>
        <a href="/volunteer" class="btn btn-secondary">Get Involved</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Discover Our Trails</h2>
        <p>Miles of scenic paths through forests and natural landscapes, maintained by our dedicated volunteer community</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">ğŸ¥¾</div>
          <h3>Hiking</h3>
          <p>Enjoy peaceful walks through wooded trails perfect for all skill levels. Experience the beauty of nature right in your neighborhood.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">ğŸš´</div>
          <h3>Mountain Biking</h3>
          <p>Multi-use trails welcome mountain bikers. Ride responsibly and share the trail with other users.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-icon">ğŸ•</div>
          <h3>Dog Walking</h3>
          <p>Bring your furry friends along! Dogs are welcome on leash. Please clean up after your pets.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background-color: var(--color-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div>
          <h2>Trail Information</h2>
          <p>The POACRE Trails Committee oversees and maintains our community trail system. These multi-use trails are open to all residents and guests of Chesapeake Ranch Estates.</p>
          
          <div class="info-box">
            <h4>ğŸ• Hours of Operation</h4>
            <p><strong>Dawn to Dusk</strong> - Year Round</p>
          </div>

          <h3>Trail Features</h3>
          <ul style="margin-left: var(--spacing-lg); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
            <li>Multiple interconnected trail loops</li>
            <li>Color-coded trail markers</li>
            <li>Benches and rest areas</li>
            <li>Natural wooded scenery</li>
            <li>Well-maintained paths</li>
          </ul>

          <a href="/rules" class="btn btn-primary">View Trail Rules</a>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>Get Involved</h2>
          <p>Our trails are maintained entirely by volunteers from our community. The POACRE Trails Committee meets several times a year to plan maintenance and improvements.</p>

          <h3>Volunteer Opportunities</h3>
          <ul style="margin-left: var(--spacing-lg); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
            <li>Trail maintenance days</li>
            <li>Clearing brush and debris</li>
            <li>Trail marking and signage</li>
            <li>Committee participation</li>
            <li>Event organization</li>
          </ul>

          <p>No special skills required - just a willingness to help keep our trails beautiful and accessible for everyone!</p>

          <a href="/volunteer" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Location & Access</h2>
        <p>Find us at Chesapeake Ranch Estates in Lusby, Maryland</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card">
