          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>ğŸ“ Contact</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:443-975-4736">(443) 975-4736</a><br>
            <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:lydia@hotmail.com">lydia@hotmail.com</a>
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-md);">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
